22
00:03:20,083 --> 00:03:22,833
Hey, Anna? How come
you joined Kaleido Stage?

23
00:03:22,916 --> 00:03:25,458
I mean, instead of
being a comedian?

24
00:03:25,541 --> 00:03:30,750
Because I love Kaleido Stage.
