I don't know. I haven't
talked to him in ten years.

33
00:03:58,083 --> 00:03:59,833
Oh, you know this guy?

34
00:03:59,916 --> 00:04:03,250
Jack Baron he's my father.

35
00:04:03,333 --> 00:04:04,416
Really?

36
