Return Anna's shoe or suffer
the revenge of the Frog-People.

39
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:25,083
He used to do this thing where
he imitated a frog or an owl,

40
00:04:25,166 --> 00:04:27,833
and it used to always
make me and my friends laugh.

41
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,708
Anna, I must speak to you.

42
00:04:39,791 --> 00:04:41,041
Who are you supposed to be?

43
