Well I don't tell anyone,

44
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:45,500
but I'm an alien from
a star called Jaga Imo.

45
00:04:45,583 --> 00:04:47,291
And my name is Jaga Imo jaga.

46
00:04:47,375 --> 00:04:49,583
Stop playing with those potatoes
so I can finish dinner.

47
00:04:49,666 --> 00:04:51,500
You got me in trouble jaga.

48
00:04:54,125 --> 00:04:55,958
But then one day...

49
00:04:59,958 --> 00:05:01,250
But why, Jack?

50
00:05:01,333 --> 00:05:03,083
Please, try to understand...

51
00:05:03,166 --> 00:05:04,583
You're leaving us?

52
00:05:04,666 --> 00:05:07,791
If I stay here like
this I'll be ruined.

53
00:05:14,541 --> 00:05:24,625
Daddy? Daddy! See you tonight!
Come home early, okay?

54
00:05:26,833 --> 00:05:30,833
But he didn't come back. That
was the last time I saw him.

55
00:05:34,125 --> 00:05:37,458
You see, my Dad's agent promised
that that he was gonna get my

56
00:05:37,541 --> 00:05:41,833
Dad his very own television
series. But I guess none of that

57
00:05:41,916 --> 00:05:46,625
ever worked out for him.
Well that's show biz, right?

58
00:05:46,708 --> 00:05:48,625
You haven't seen him
at all in ten years?

59
00:05:48,708 --> 00:05:51,625
Nope, not even once. Every
once in a while he'll send me

60
