a Christmas card. I've
written him a few times, too,

61
00:05:54,333 --> 00:05:57,375
but he's always moved before
my letters could get to him.

62
00:05:59,666 --> 00:06:01,875
So that's why you're always
checking the listings for

63
00:06:01,958 --> 00:06:04,041
the Comedy Theatre. You
never know when your Father

64
00:06:04,125 --> 00:06:06,541
might come to town again.

65
00:06:06,625 --> 00:06:08,916
Well yeah, maybe that's
one reason for it,

66
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,416
but I do really love comedy and
I like knowing who's in town.

67
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:16,291
Hey, uh isn't that theatre
really close to us you guys?

68
00:06:16,375 --> 00:06:17,166
Well?

69
00:06:17,250 --> 00:06:19,583
Right. We should go see his act.

70
00:06:20,583 --> 00:06:22,666
I don't know, you guys,
part of me wants to see my Dad,

71
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:24,333
but part of me is scared.

72
00:06:24,416 --> 00:06:27,333
Then we'll accompany you,
Your Highness!

73
00:06:31,166 --> 00:06:34,875
Quit it! I told you to stop
putting your hand in my back!

74
00:06:37,083 --> 00:06:39,500
Why are you just sitting there?!
He's trying to kill me!

75
00:06:39,583 --> 00:06:42,500
This is exciting!
Will your dad recognize you?

76
00:06:42,583 --> 00:06:46,041
Oh, I'm sure he will.
He's gonna be so surprised!

77
00:06:50,333 --> 00:06:52,208
Oh, you're too kind.

78
00:06:52,291 --> 00:06:54,875
Hey, thank the nice folks,
then get off stage.

79
00:06:54,958 --> 00:06:58,083
Right. Thank you very much.

80
00:06:58,166 --> 00:06:59,958
Hey, use your own voice,
you moron!

81
00:07:02,291 --> 00:07:04,458
Now it's time for our next
act, and the show can only

82
00:07:04,541 --> 00:07:07,666
get better, right?
Just kidding, folks!

83
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:10,291
Ladies and gentlemen, please
welcome to the stage the one,

84
00:07:10,375 --> 00:07:12,708
the only, Jack Baron!

85
00:07:20,166 --> 00:07:23,625
That last guys been using the
same material for twenty years.

86
00:07:23,708 --> 00:07:25,875
The only thing that's different
is he's got less hair and

87
00:07:25,958 --> 00:07:28,375
the puppet's got
a full set of dentures.

88
00:07:29,291 --> 00:07:30,458
But then again,

89
00:07:30,541 --> 00:07:32,375
I guess the audiences
have gone downhill, too.

90
00:07:36,208 --> 00:07:37,500
What's wrong?

91
